Package uk.ac.manchester.spinnaker.machine.board

package uk.ac.manchester.spinnaker.machine.board
Classes relating to boards in a SpiNNaker machine. Note that boards themselves mostly not modelled, but their coordinates schemes are because they are used in many places.
